name: Danny Ocean
description:
'''Daniel Alejandro Morales Reyes''' (born 5 May 1992), known by his stage name '''Danny Ocean''', is a [[Venezuela]]n singer, songwriter and record producer born in [[Caracas|Caracas, Venezuela]]. He began his professional music career in 2009 with the creation of his [[YouTube]] channel.

He is best known for his song "[[Me Reh√∫so]]", released in September 2016, and relaunched as an English version titled "Baby I Won't" in 2017.
